message.body: Hey, what are you up to tonight? I'm working till about 10, but wanna find something to do afterwards?
Tried to find some music but didnt see anything good

Hmm sure, but can I see how tired I feel? I have a friend coming into town early tomorrow, though I was thinking about maybe seeing a movie tonight. Also, west phila orchestra is playing Tuesday- want to go? I think tickets are 15 b
Yes, yes and yes. Any movies showing around 9?
Hiroshima mom amour 9:30, bird man 9:40, theory of everything 9:50
Birdman is amazing, id see it again. Also want to see rosewater, i dont know anything about the othera
Bird man it is. That's probably at the top of my list
Ritz five. I'll probably walk over if we meet there.
I finished up delivering and im a few blocks away, should i meet you at you apt?
Hey just about to leave my apt, where are you?
Im at 9th and south, ill head to you
